import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { useNavigate, Link } from 'react-router-dom'; // Import Link import { Container, Typography, Card, CardContent, Button, Select, MenuItem, FormControl, InputLabel, Grid, IconButton } from '@mui/material'; // Add all needed Material UI imports import { List, ListItem, ListItemText } from '@mui/material'; // Add this line for List, ListItem, and ListItemText import MenuIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Menu'; import ExitToAppIcon from '@mui/icons-material/ExitToApp'; import AccountBalanceWalletIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AccountBalanceWallet'; import GroupIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Group'; import GroupAddIcon from '@mui/icons-material/GroupAdd'; import AccountCircleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/AccountCircle'; import RuleIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Rule'; import HelpOutlineIcon from '@mui/icons-material/HelpOutline'; import SecurityIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Security'; import AssignmentIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Assignment'; import FooterMenu from '../Footer.jsx'; // Import FooterMenu component import './Team.css'; // Import the CSS file const Team = () => { const navigate = useNavigate(); // Hook to navigate between pages const [teamData, setTeamData] = useState({ registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00, cumulativeTeamSize: 0, generations: [ { percentage: 18, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00, }, { percentage: 6, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00, }, { percentage: 3, teamCommission: 0, registeredMembers: 0, validMembers: 0, teamIncome: 0.00, }, ], }); const [filter, setFilter] = useState('All'); const [menuOpen, setMenuOpen] = useState(false); const handleFilterChange = (event) => { setFilter(event.target.value); }; const handleViewTeamList = () => { navigate('/team-list'); }; const toggleMenu = () => { setMenuOpen(!menuOpen); }; const logout = () => { // Implement logout functionality here }; return (
{/* Header with Burger Icon and Logout Button */}
{/* Side Menu */}
{/* Main Content */} My Team {/* Filter Section */} My Team Overview Filter {/* Team Data Overview */} Registered Members {teamData.registeredMembers} Valid Members {teamData.validMembers} Team Income ${teamData.teamIncome.toFixed(2)} {/* Cumulative Team Size and View Team List */} Cumulative Team Size: {teamData.cumulativeTeamSize} {/* Generations Data (Horizontal Cards, Vertically Aligned Content Inside) */} The Last Three Generations of Data {teamData.generations.map((generation, index) => ( {`Generation ${index + 1}`} Percentage: {generation.percentage}% Team Commission: ${generation.teamCommission} Registered Members: {generation.registeredMembers} Valid Members: {generation.validMembers} Team Income: ${generation.teamIncome.toFixed(2)} ))}
{/* Footer */}
); }; export default Team;
